description: This is an excel table for the 2011 TANF and Separate State Program - Maintenance of Effort (SSP-MOE) Caseload Data which includes the following data elements: Total Number of Recipients, Total Number of Families, Total Number of Children, 1-Parent Families, 2-Parent Families, 0-Parent Families, Total Number of Adults.

title: 2011 Temporary Assistance for Needy Families Caseload Data - Number of Families and Recipients
